cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.DB

This paper deals with the identification of users across multiple devices, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes a method for matching cookies to devices, which is a topic related to databases (cs.DB). Finally, the paper discusses the challenge of developing efficient applications in a multi-device world, which is a topic related to social and information networks (cs.SI).
